sql:
SELECT country_name, iso_code
FROM countries
ORDER BY country_name ASC;

external_knowledge:
- "Vaccination rate" refers to the percentage of the population that has received at least one dose of a COVID-19 vaccine;
- "Rankings" imply the relative position of a country within its continent based on vaccination rate and hospitalization numbers;
- The data is ordered to facilitate comparison of countries' performance within their respective continents.
